      "Description": "Allows for DesignScript code to be authored directly",
      "Code": "newl;\noldl;\nres = [Imperative]{\nif (oldl != null)\n{\n\treturn = SetDifference(newl, oldl);\n}\nelse\n{\n\treturn = newl;\n}\n};"
